{"data":[{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"0_1733214867.898126","card_id":"Q_5545042556","target":{"id":5545042556,"title":"魔芋爽击败辣条成为卫龙营收「顶梁柱」，为啥魔芋制品这么火？宣称「低卡低脂」的魔芋食品真能减脂吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/5545042556","type":"question","created":1732933795,"answer_count":110,"follower_count":313,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[81958,101935,105508,163884,2336296],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"曾经靠辣条打下零食圈半壁江山的卫龙，最先尝到魔芋爽的甜头。 自2014年推出魔芋爽以来，这个被寄予厚望的“小儿子”的营收就一路走高，终于在今年，反超自己的辣条“大哥”，成为卫龙家族里的营收顶梁柱——卫龙2024年中期财务报告显示，魔芋产品营收占总收入49.7%，超过日渐式微的辣条。 魔芋爽能够拿下如此高营收的一个重要的原因是足够高的毛利率。根据卫龙的财报，今年上半年，蔬菜制品（魔芋制品）的毛利率达到了52%，高于调味面制品（辣条为主）的47%。 每日人物：打工人的“下饭搭子”魔芋，是下一个“零食之王”吗？"},"attached_info":"CkEI8bH3pP21vMcwEAMaCTExMjA4NTUxOSCj8am6BjAAOLkCQAByCjU1NDUwNDI1NTZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"690 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8507f0b0b3aea034b0070312016a2992_r.jpg?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"1_1733214867.899572","card_id":"Q_660954783","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":660954783,"title":"如何证明2π+e>9?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/660954783","type":"question","created":1720314867,"answer_count":80,"follower_count":134,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1291,92654],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"不能用计算器"},"attached_info":"CkAI8bH3pP21vMcwEAMaCTEwOTE1NjQ1NSDz16e0BjAAOIYBQAFyCTY2MDk1NDc4M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"237 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"chil